"{\"uid\": \"en.shafaqna.com-377315-aa-sabotage-hits-french-railway-network-before-olympics\", \"text\": \"ShafaqnaEnglish-The sabotage on railways in France had \\\"massive and serious\\\" impacts, France's outgoing Prime Minister said.  \\\"Early this morning, acts of sabotage were carried out, in a prepared and coordinated way, on SNCF facilities,\\\" Gabriel Attal wrote on X. \\\"The results on the railway network are massive and serious.\\\"Attal thanked the firefighters who intervened and the SNCF employees who are working to re-establish the network.  \\\"Our intelligence services and security forces are mobilized to find and punish the authors of those criminal acts,\\\" the premier added.  Source:Anadolu Ajansi          Save my name, email, and website in this browser for the next time I comment.      \\u0394\"}"